Package io.sf.carte.doc.style.css

Interface LABColorValue

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, CSSColorValue, CSSPrimitiveValue, CSSTypedValue, CSSValue
All Known Implementing Classes:
LABColorValue
public interface LABColorValue extends CSSColorValue
Represents a Lab (lab()) color value.

Instead of using this interface, you may want to just cast the result of CSSColorValue.getColor() to the appropriate interface (like LABColor) according to the given CSSColorValue.getColorModel().
